name: Get It Filled
description:
Are you able to fill all the tiles and finish on the green mark to complete the level? 
Can you solve all 80 levels? Give it a try!

Update: 40 new levels added!
(And a mobile version is probably coming)


Use the mouse or keyboard to control the player.
Specific keyboard controls:

  • Arrow keys: move the player
  • Arrow keys + Shift: keep moving
  • Spacebar: undo one step
  • R: restart the level
  • M: mute music
  • S: mute sounds
  • A: go to previous level
  • Z: go to next level
